6.3 C/C++
=========

 -- Flycheck Syntax Checker: c/c++ -clang

          Chained syntax checkers: The following syntax checkers are
          *note chained: 57. after this syntax checker:

            1. *note c/c++-cppcheck: a3, if there are no errors above
